satellite/000000/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban intersection. The central focus is a curved road with a few vehicles moving along it, suggesting light traffic. On the left, there is a parking area with several cars, bordered by green patches and trees. To the right, a large paved surface, possibly a sports field or open lot, lies adjacent to the road. The surrounding area includes buildings and more greenery. The image appears to be taken on an overcast day, with flat lighting and no distinct shadows. Overall, the scene feels calm and orderly, with no signs of rush or activity.

satellite/000000/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a curved road intersection in an urban area. The road bends from the left to the right, with a smooth gray surface and white dashed lines marking the lanes. A few vehicles are visible on the road, moving slowly, suggesting light traffic. On the left side of the image, there is a large building with a curved glass facade, possibly a shopping center or office complex, reflecting some light. Behind it, a small parking area contains a few cars. On the right, a rectangular structure with a flat roof appears to be an industrial or commercial building surrounded by trees and greenery. The surrounding area has patches of dark green trees and manicured landscaping. There are no visible people or signs of rain, and the lighting is uniform, suggesting an overcast or slightly cloudy day. The image has a calm and quiet atmosphere, lacking any sense of urgency. The scene feels organized but subdued, like a typical day in a modern city.

satellite/000000/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a road intersection in an urban area. In the center, a curved road cuts through the scene, with a few vehicles moving along it. To the left, there is a large open area with a gray building and several parked cars. The area around the road is mostly filled with gray asphalt and some patches of green trees and bushes. On the right, more buildings and green spaces are visible, along with a sidewalk running parallel to the road. The image is clear, with good visibility and no signs of rain or heavy cloud cover. The lighting suggests it is taken during the day under bright conditions. The overall atmosphere is calm and functional, typical of a quiet city corner. There are no people visible, and the scene appears orderly and well-maintained. The colors are mostly neutral—grays, greens, and dark roads—giving the scene a clean and structured look. The image captures a peaceful moment in a developed neighborhood, with the buildings and roads forming a neatly organized layout.

satellite/000001/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a curved road with a bridge-like structure. The road runs diagonally across the frame, with vehicles visible on it, moving along the curve. To the left, there is open ground with some green patches, possibly trees. On the right, part of a large building with a flat roof and some flat rectangular sections stands near the road. The scene is captured under overcast lighting, giving the image a muted, grayish tone. The overall impression is calm and quiet, with no signs of heavy traffic or activity.

satellite/000001/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a curved road surrounded by green areas and buildings. In the center of the image, a dark asphalt road bends from the lower left toward the upper right, with visible white lane markings. A small white vehicle can be seen on the road, heading toward the curve. To the right of the road, a large structure with a flat roof stands, possibly a building or a parking garage. The surrounding area includes patches of trees and shrubs, giving the scene a mix of natural and urban elements. On the left, a quieter section shows open ground and possibly a parking lot. The image appears taken during daylight with soft lighting, suggesting overcast weather, as there are no sharp shadows. The colors are muted—grays of the pavement, greens of the trees, and browns of the soil. The overall atmosphere is calm and neutral, with no signs of heavy traffic or activity. The high-angle view gives a clear sense of the layout of the area.

satellite/000001/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a suburban area featuring a curved road with light traffic. In the center, the road bends gently from the bottom left toward the top right, lined with what appear to be streetlights and some trees. To the right of the road, there is a rectangular building with a flat roof and small rooftop structures, possibly a utility or commercial facility. On the left, a larger area of open land with scattered trees and pavement is visible, possibly a parking lot or recreational space. In the upper portion of the image, a large, long rectangular structure—likely a sports field or open arena—can be seen, bordered by a paved track. The scene is captured in broad daylight with no visible shadows, indicating a cloudy or overcast sky, which gives the image a flat, diffused light. The colors are muted, consisting mostly of gray asphalt, green vegetation, and brown patches of earth, creating a calm and quiet atmosphere. The overall impression is one of a well-organized but quiet urban fringe, with minimal activity and a sense of stillness.

satellite/000002/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a curved road and several buildings. On the left, a road with visible lanes and a vehicle curves through the scene. To the right, there are multiple low-rise structures, possibly warehouses or industrial buildings, with flat roofs and rectangular shapes. A few smaller side roads intersect the main road, creating a network of paths. The ground is a mix of paved surfaces and patches of greenery, which appear dark due to the lighting. A partial view of a taller structure can be seen on the far right edge. The image appears to be taken during the day under overcast conditions, with no clear shadows, giving the scene a flat, muted look. The overall view is minimal and functional, typical of a cityscape viewed from above.

satellite/000002/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city showing roads, green areas, and buildings. In the center of the image, there is a large structure with flat rooftops, possibly a commercial or institutional building, surrounded by paved surfaces and what appear to be parking spaces. To the left, a curved road cuts through the scene, with vehicles visible along its length, suggesting light traffic movement. The area near the top of the image contains a mix of trees and open space, indicating a park or landscaped zone. On the right side, a higher structure with a tiered design stands, possibly part of a larger complex. The image is taken during the day under clear conditions, with no visible clouds or rain, providing good visibility of the scene. The overall tone is neutral and functional, reflecting a typical urban environment viewed from above. The colors are mostly muted, with shades of gray and brown dominating the urban features, contrasted by patches of green from trees and shrubs. There is no strong sense of human activity, giving the scene a calm and distant appearance.

satellite/000002/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a suburban area with roads, buildings, and green spaces. In the center, a curved road runs diagonally from the top left to the bottom right, bordered by trees and a sidewalk. On the right side, a large rectangular building with a flat roof stands, appearing to have multiple windows and clear structural lines; it could be a school or office complex. To the left of the road, a parking lot with marked spaces is visible, though no cars are present. There are patches of grass and shrubs in the area, suggesting some landscaping. Smaller buildings and structures are scattered around, appearing more residential. The image is taken in daylight with clear visibility, no signs of rain, fog, or clouds. The overall scene feels calm and organized, with a quiet, functional atmosphere typical of a developed neighborhood. The colors are muted—gray roads, brown earth tones, and dark green foliage—giving the image a subdued and practical appearance.
